{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7f80652e71","title":"关于批判黑《修养》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5036a67730","index":1,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"7f80652e71","article":{}},{"id":"9fbb4834bc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"7f80652e71","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b917deee93","type":"title","text":"关于批判黑《修养》","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ef37c0064","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d6a012265","type":"paragraph","text":"千万不要再上《修养》那本书的当。《修养》这本书，是欺人之谈，脱离现实的阶级斗争，脱离革命，脱离政治斗争，闭口不谈革命的根本问题是政权问题，闭口不谈无产阶级专政问题，宣扬唯心主义的修养论，转弯抹角地提倡资产阶级个人主义，提倡奴隶主义，反对马克思列宁主义、毛泽东思想。按照这本书去“修养”，只能是越养越“修”，越修养越成为修正主义。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29e244f9bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（转摘自《红旗》杂志一九六七年第五期评沦员文章）","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33af05fb64","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd17e58a3e","type":"paragraph","text":"这本书完全是欺人之谈。革命的基本问题，就是政权问题。到底要不要夺取政权，能不能夺取政权，怎样夺取政权，对于这些基本问题，这个小册子（即《修养》）避而不谈。根本不谈夺取政权，不谈无产阶级专政，离开了政权，离开了阶级，离开了阶级分析，离开了阶级斗争，完全是一本资产阶级唯心主义的、反动的、不触及蒋介石一根毫毛的东西，是一株资产阶级的大毒草。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19b6c581bf","type":"subdate","text":"（四月十三日康生同志在军委扩大会议上的讲话）","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab93766789","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63cc8a8a91","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇的《论共产党员的修养》我看过几遍，这是反马列主义的。我看大学生应该更好的研究一下，选几段写文章批判。要批判刘少奇的《沦共产党员的修养》和邓小平多年来的讲话。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c67410e8ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4534e91f18","type":"paragraph","text":"四月七日《北京日报》社论《打倒反动的“驯服工具论”》发表的当天，毛主席说：我从来就不同意“驯服工具论”。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9224ad1b26","type":"subdate","text":"（四月九日传达）","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"7f80652e71","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":577,"end":576}}}},"__N_SSG":true}